@startuml
left to right direction
actor 客户 as C
actor 门店店员 as Clerk
actor 门店店长 as Manager
actor 总部运营管理员 as HQ
actor 财务人员 as Fin
actor 配送外协人员 as Delivery
actor 系统管理员 as SysAdmin

rectangle 图文快印门店连锁管理系统 {
  usecase UC_Submit as 提交订单与文件
  usecase UC_Check as 文件合规校验
  usecase UC_Quote as 录入参数与报价
  usecase UC_Calc as 阶梯价自动计算
  usecase UC_Discount as 折扣特批
  usecase UC_Dispatch as 排产调度
  usecase UC_Route as 跨店派单路由
  usecase UC_Emergency as 应急开关放行
  usecase UC_Deliver as 执行配送任务
  usecase UC_Pickup as 取件确认
  usecase UC_Invoice as 发票开具与红冲
  usecase UC_Reconcile as 日结对账
  usecase UC_Config as 权限与路由配置

  C --> UC_Submit
  Clerk --> UC_Quote
  Manager --> UC_Discount
  Manager --> UC_Dispatch
  HQ --> UC_Route
  Fin --> UC_Invoice
  Fin --> UC_Reconcile
  Delivery --> UC_Deliver
  SysAdmin --> UC_Config
  C --> UC_Pickup

  UC_Submit ..> UC_Check : include
  UC_Quote ..> UC_Calc : include
  UC_Dispatch ..> UC_Route : include
  UC_Discount .> UC_Quote : extend
  UC_Emergency .> UC_Dispatch : extend
  UC_Invoice .> UC_Pickup : extend
  UC_Reconcile ..> UC_Invoice : include
}
@enduml
